markdownRemark.html: I've always been a fan of photography, and art in general. I first remember really getting into taking pictures when I discovered the manual settings on my parents digital SLR camera. Nowadays, I like shooting 35mm film in a Canon AE-1 that I got from eBay or other cheap cameras I find at thrift stores. Someday I'll buy a more expensive camera image 1 image 2 image 3 image 4 ...
